title: The God Who Overrules | Joel Osteen
itunes:title: The God Who Overrules | Joel Osteen
description:
What’s stopped you in the past is not going to stop you anymore. God can overturn any negative situation in your life. He wants to deliver you from anything that's holding you back. 


Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
